<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">76倍速算法，76与某数（40以内）相乘时，某数若是4的几倍，积的首两位数字就是某数的四分之三倍值，末两位数则是某数本身。可用公式</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">(n×4)×76=n×300+4n</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">进行速算，其中某数为n×4（n为任意正整数）。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">76×24=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 76×24</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=6×300+4×6</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=1800+24</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=1824</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>